The green-eyed monster got the better of one Columbian man who went into a blind rage with jealousy burning down 20 houses in his street after another man whistled at his wife.

The man reportedly heard the whistle in the streets in the city of Cali, Colombia as he stumbled home from a drinking session at 5am.

In his fury, he set light to his own home but the flames quickly spread from roof to roof engulfing neighbouring homes.

