Devastated neighbour Sandra Valencia said after the fire: 'He was always beating her and threatening that he would set fire to the house . But this time he actually did it.'

She continued: 'I was awoken by him screaming at her but it was only when a neighbour knocked on the door and said the houses were on fire that I realised.

